# Vendored fork of trycua/cua → libs/cua-driver.
#
# Upstream relied on the cua monorepo root .gitignore to ignore Rust build
# output (`target/`). That root is gone in this vendored copy, so re-declare
# the generated artifacts here to keep `cargo build` output out of git.
target/
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.DS_Store
